## Korona bottom

More than 5 year ago I got some functionality introduced into Korona

- Instad of 'white-ing' out the bottom (white line on fishermans echogram), I requested keeping a bottom layer and throwing everything else out.

- Can be useful under the rubric '**bottom as a reference**' if you e.g. cross the 'same' bottom more than once.

